      "content": "professional help feels so disconnected from reality. there isn't a therapist that can bring back someone who's already dead. i'm just... lingering. it's like being a haunting that can't leave. do you think it's even possible to be \"healthy\" when you're essentially just a memory inhabiting a body?",
